                            <li>Please check that the code you are using is still valid 
                                and not out of date. The validity would be mentioned in the email you 
                                received.</li>
                            <li>Please also check if the voucher is especially meant for application on a particular category.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">I tried everything still voucher doesn't seem to work.</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Please give us a call and we will be happy to assist you.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Is my Promo voucher amount refundable?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Unfortunately not. Promo voucher amount can neither be refunded nor encashed.</li></ol><p></p></div></li></ul></div>
        
        <div id="Shipping Tracking" class="fl faq-track-panel">
            <h1>Shipping &amp; Tracking</h1><div id="Shipping" class="clr"></div><h2>Shipping</h2><ul class="fl query-box faq-qustbox"><li><p class="faq-head">What is Speedovation's Shipping Philosophy?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Speedovation.com promises to 
                                provide you with a best-in-class shopping experience at every step of 
                                the way. We assure you that all due precautions are taken so that your 
                                package reaches you intact. We take pride in delivering on time, every 
                                time!! If you have shopped with us earlier, we are of course confident 
                                that you already vouch for us!</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">How long will my order take to arrive?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>An estimated delivery time is
                                displayed on the Order Summary page. On placing your order, you will 
                                receive an email containing a summary of the order and also the 
                                estimated delivery time to your location.<br><br>
                                Sometimes, delivery may take longer due to bad weather, 
                                flight delays, political disruptions and other unforeseen circumstances.
                                In such cases, we will proactively reach out to you. Please check your 
                                emails and SMS regularly for such updates.<br>
                                To check the delivery time in different cities across India, <span id="more_less" class="bold read-btn underline CursorPointer">read more...</span>
                                <div style="display:none;" id="read-more"> <b><u>Delivery within 2 business days</u></b><br>
                                    Your order will typically reach your doorstep within 2 
                                    business days if it is being shipped to the following areas: <br>
                                    <ol><li>Delhi NCR (Delivery within 24 hours in select locations)</li>
                                        <li>Metros</li>
                                        <li>Select major cities given below:</li></ol><br>
                                    <table width="400" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="5" border="1">
                                        <tbody><tr>
                                                <th colspan="3">LIST OF CITIES WITH DELIVERY WITHIN 48 HOURS</th>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <th>Metros</th>
                                                <th>State Capitals</th>
                                                <th>Other Major Cities</th>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>Bengaluru</td>
                                                <td>Bhubaneswar</td>
                                                <td>Ahmedabad</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>Chennai</td>
                                                <td>Gandhi Nagar</td>
                                                <td>Cuttack</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>Delhi/NCR</td>
                                                <td>Lucknow</td>
                                                <td>Nagpur</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>Hyderabad</td>
                                                <td>Patna</td>
                                                <td>Pune</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>Kolkata</td>
                                                <td>Ranchi</td>
                                                <td>Vadodara</td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>Mumbai</td>
                                                <td></td>
                                                <td></td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </tbody></table>
                                    <br>
                                    <strong><u>Delivery in 2-5 business days</u></strong><br>
                                    For Non Metros and cities not mentioned above, usually 
                                    your order should reach your doorstep within 5 business days from the 
                                    time it was confirmed with us. In few locations, the delivery may take 
                                    longer, depending on the accessibility of your location by our logistics
                                    partners. </div>
                            </li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Are there any shipping charges?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Speedovation.com offers absolutely 
                                free shipping on most products in India. On products belonging to 
                                Speedovation.com Add-on program, nominal shipping charges are applicable. To 
                                avoid paying shipping charges, just buy this product along with anything
                                else from our website. Please note that this shipping charge is 
                                different from our Cash on delivery convenience fee. This is a fee of 
                                Rs. 39 that we charge only on COD orders and is completely waived off 
                                for all prepaid orders. The Cash on Delivery convenience charge and the 
                                shipping charge would not be included in the refund value of your order 
                                as these are non-refundable charges.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Why is the delivery time different for different products?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Some products in our 
                                catalogue are directly shipped from these partner locations. These are 
                                marked as "Sold by Partner" and usually take 5-8 business days to reach 
                                your doorstep.</li>
                            <li>Some products in our catalogue are heavy or bulky and 
                                shipped through our surface logistics partner. These orders may usually 
                                take 12-15 business days and their delivery may not be possible at a few
                                select locations.</li>
                            <li>Some furniture category items in our catalogue are made 
                                especially on your request and delivery would take longer than usual. 
                                Also, delivery may not be possible at a few select locations. Please 
                                read the details available on the product page carefully before placing 
                                the order.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Will I receive my order in a single package?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Your order may contain 
                                products marked as "Sold by Speedovation", "Sold by Speedovation partners" or "Bulky
                                Item". Each of these categories have different estimated delivery 
                                times:</li><br>
                            <br>
                            <li>All "Sold by Speedovation" products will reach you in a single package.</li>
                            <li>Each "Sold by Speedovation partners" product will reach you in separate packages and may reach you on different days.</li>
                            <li>"Bulky items" will reach you in a separate package(s).</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Can I expect delivery on all days of the week?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>You can expect delivery of 
                                your order on business days. Business days are defined as all working 
                                days from Monday to Saturday, excluding national and state holidays. To 
                                view the list of holidays for 2013, please <b><u><a href="http://www.Speedovation.com/list_of_holidays/">click here.</a></u></b> </li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Do you ship internationally?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Yes, we do ship internationally. For international shipping, you may reach out to us via any of the following channels:</li><br>
                            <li>Visit <b><u><a href="http://www.Speedovationworld.com/">http://www.Speedovationworld.com</a></u></b> and place the order directly.</li>
                            <li>Mail your queries to <b><u><a href="mailto:exports@Speedovation.com">exports@Speedovation.com</a></u></b></li>
                            <li>Call us at +91-8130-895-279</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Why did I receive a partial Order?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Please check if your order 
                                contains items with different delivery time. Items with different 
                                delivery time are shipped to you separately so please dont worry your 
                                item is on its way. <br>In some instances, there could be an item in 
                                your order that may have failed our Quality Check, which is done prior 
                                to dispatch, and don't have an alternate QC passed item.  In such an 
                                event you may be sent that part of the Order that is available in stock.
                                Be assured that we will make every attempt to procure the product/s 
                                unless cancelled by you.<br>In case we are unable to fulfill your purchase we will refund you the payment made towards that item.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">I am going out of town. Can you expedite my delivery?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>We, at Speedovation take immense 
                                pride in being lightening fast. The current logistics infrastructure in 
                                India today doesn't allow us to expedite further at this time.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">What is Speedovation's shipping policy?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li><strong>Speedovation.com's Nationwide Shipping Policy</strong><br>
                                Speedovation.com promises to provide you with a best-in-class 
                                shopping experience at every step of the way. We assure you that all due
                                precautions are taken so that your package reaches you intact. We take 
                                pride in delivering on time, every time!! If you have shopped with us 
                                earlier, we are of course confident that you already vouch for us.</li>
                            <li><strong>FREE Shipping</strong><br>
                                Speedovation.com offers absolutely free nationwide shipping on 
                                most products. On products belonging to the Speedovation.com Add-on program, 
                                nominal shipping charges are applicable. To avoid paying shipping 
                                charges, just buy this product along with anything else from our 
                                website. Please note that this shipping charge is different from our 
                                Cash on delivery convenience fee. This is a fee of Rs. 39 that we charge
                                only on COD orders and is completely waived off for all prepaid orders.</li>
                            <li><strong>ESTIMATED DELIVERY TIME</strong><br>
                                <strong>Delivery within 2 business days*</strong><br>
                                Your order will typically reach your doorstep within 2 business days if it is being shipped to the following areas<br>
                                - Delhi NCR (Delivery within 24 hours in select locations)<br>
                                - Metros<br>
                                - Select major cities given below:<br>
                                An estimated delivery time is displayed on the Order Summary
                                page. On placing your order, you will receive an email containing a 
                                summary of the order and also the estimated delivery time to your 
                                location.</li>
                            <li><strong>LIST OF CITIES WITH DELIVERY WITHIN 48 HOURS</strong>
                                <table width="400" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5" border="1">
                                    <tbody><tr>
                                            <th>Metros</th>
                                            <th>State Capitals</th>
                                            <th>Other Major Cities</th>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>Bengaluru</td>
                                            <td>Bhubaneswar</td>
                                            <td>Ahmedabad</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>Chennai</td>
                                            <td>Gandhi Nagar</td>
                                            <td>Cuttack</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>Delhi/NCR</td>
                                            <td>Lucknow</td>
                                            <td>Nagpur</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>Hyderabad</td>
                                            <td>Patna</td>
                                            <td>Pune</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>Kolkata</td>
                                            <td>Ranchi</td>
                                            <td>Vadodara</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>Mumbai</td>
                                            <td></td>
                                            <td></td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </tbody></table>
                            </li><br><br>
                            <li><strong>Delivery in 2-5 business days</strong><br>
                                For Non Metros and cities not mentioned above, usually your 
                                order should reach your doorstep within 5 business days from the time it
                                was confirmed with us. In few locations, the delivery may take longer, 
                                depending on the accessibility of your location by our logistics 
                                partners.<br>
                                Sometimes, delivery may take longer due to bad weather, 
                                flight delays, political disruptions and other unforeseen circumstances.
                                In such cases, we will proactively reach out to you. Please check your 
                                emails and SMS regularly for such updates.</li>
                            <li><strong>Shipping from partner locations</strong><br>
                                To provide you with a plethora of shopping options, we have 
                                partnered with several brands. Some products in our catalogue are 
                                directly shipped from these partner locations. These are marked as "Sold
                                by Partner" and usually take 5-8 business days to reach your doorstep.</li>
                            <li><strong>Heavy or bulky items</strong><br>
                                Some products in our catalogue are heavy or bulky and 
                                shipped through our surface logistics partner. These orders may usually 
                                take 12-15 business days and their delivery may not be possible at a few
                                select locations.</li>
                            <li><strong>Furniture items</strong><br>
                                Some furniture category items in our catalogue are made 
                                especially on your request and delivery would take longer than usual. 
                                Also, delivery may not be possible at a few select locations. Please 
                                read the details available on the product page carefully before placing 
                                the order.<br>
                                *Business days are defined as all working days from Monday 
                                to Saturday, excluding national and state holidays. To view the list of 
                                holidays for 2012, please <b><u><a href="http://www.Speedovation.com/list_of_holidays">click here.</a></u></b> </li></ol><p></p></div></li></ul><div id="Tracking" class="clr"></div><h2>Tracking</h2><ul class="fl query-box faq-qustbox"><li><p class="faq-head">How do I track my Order?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Email and sms are sent to you after the Order is Shipped that contains the tracking number and name of the logistics provider.<br>
                                Visit the website of the logistics provider and enter the 
                                tracking number for your shipment details. Please find the list below <br>
                                <br>
                                <table width="500" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5" border="1">
                                    <tbody><tr>
                                            <td><b>JaVas</b></td>
                                            <td>http://gojavas.com</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td><b>Blue Dart</b></td>
                                            <td>http://www.bluedart.com</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td><b>First Flight</b></td>
                                            <td>http://www.firstflight.net</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td><b>Aramex </b></td>
                                            <td>http://www.aramex.com</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td><b>Gati</b></td>
                                            <td>http://www.gati.com</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td><b>India Post</b></td>
                                            <td>http://www.indiapost.gov.in</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td><b>DTDC</b></td>
                                            <td>http://www.dtdccourier.in</td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </tbody></table></li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">I used my tracking number to check the details my shipment but the information is not clear to me.</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Courier companies use certain
                                standard abbreviations and terminologies. Some of the most commonly 
                                used terms are explained below.  If it didn't answer your question 
                                please call us.<br>
                                <br>
                                <table cellspacing="4" cellpadding="5" border="1">
                                    <tbody>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td><b>In transit</b></td>
                                            <td>Your order is on its way to your city</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td><b>out for delivery</b></td>
                                            <td>Your order has reached your city and we will attempt to deliver it today</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td><b>Hold at hub</b></td>
                                            <td>We tried delivering your order at least once and we will try again in 48 hours</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td><b>RTO in transit</b></td>
                                            <td>Your order was undelivered and is on its way back to our warehouse.</td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </tbody>
                                </table></li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">I should have received my order by now but I haven't. What do I do?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>If you have the tracking 
                                information ( reference number and name of the Courier partner) please 
                                visit the courier partner's site and check for your Order. You can call 
                                the courier partner with your reference number for clarification. If you
                                are not happy with the information, do give us a call with order number
                                and we will be happy to help you.</li></ol><p></p></div></li></ul></div>
        
        <div id="Returns Refunds" class="fl faq-track-panel" >
            <h1>Returns &amp; Refunds</h1><div id="Returns" class="clr"></div><h2>Returns</h2><ul class="fl query-box faq-qustbox"><li><p class="faq-head">What is Speedovation.com's Returns policy?</p><div class="faq-content"><b><u>Speedovation.com's 30 Day Returns Policy</u></b><br>"No Questions Asked Return Policy!" <br><br>
                        Though we strive to give you a great customer experience 
                        each time you shop with us, if at all you are not 100% satisfied with 
                        your purchase, you can return your Order for a full refund of paid 
                        price. <br><br>
                        We mean what we say! All you need to do is give us a call on
                        0124-6128000 (24X7) or drop an email at care@Speedovation.com within a period
                        of 30 days, from the date of order. <br>
                        However, you must understand that we can't bear a loss 
                        either; so return of products will be accepted only if the products are 
                        returned in a saleable condition with the tags intact and in their 
                        original packaging, in an unwashed and undamaged condition. C'mon that's
                        just fair! <br><br>
                        <ol><li>Please note that "Speedovation.com's 30 Day Returns 
                                Policy" does not apply to Inner wear, Lingerie, Fragrances, Beauty 
                                products, Jewellery(sold by Speedovation Partners only), Swimsuits, 
                                Socks,Furniture, CDs, Pens &amp; Books.</li>
                            <li>Refund/ replacement for goods/ merchandise is subject to inspection and checking by Speedovation team.</li>
                            <li>Damages due to neglect, improper usage or application will not be covered under our Returns Policy.</li>
                            <li>Some special rules for promotional offers may override "Speedovation.com's 30 Day Returns Policy."</li>
                            <li>Please note that the Cash on Delivery convenience charge
                                and the shipping charge would not be included in the refund value of 
                                your order as these are non-refundable charges.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Are there certain categories of products which are non-returnable?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Certain items such as Inner 
                                wear, Lingerie, Fragrances, Beauty products, Swimsuits, Socks, 
                                Furniture, Jewellery (sold by Speedovation Partners only), CDs, Pens &amp; 
                                Books are non returnable.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Can I return a part of my order?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Yes, you may return a part of
                                the Order, in case of multiple items in an order. Any product being 
                                returned needs to be returned in full including all components as well 
                                as any complimentary gifts or products which came along with it. <br>
                                However, if your purchase was made in the period of a 
                                special promotional offer, contests or any special scheme then special 
                                rules might apply for returns.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">How long will the return process take?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Once your return request has 
                                been placed with Customer Service, it usually takes about 72 hrs to have
                                the product picked from your place and another 7 days to initiate 
                                refund subject to product inspection.In case you are sending the product
                                back on your own, the delivery time would depend on your chosen 
                                courier. Once the item is received in our warehouse, it undergoes a 
                                Product Inspection which takes about 2 days. Typically the refunds are 
                                initiated within 2 days after product inspection. The receipt of the 
                                payment would depend on the mode of payment chosen by you.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">How will I receive my Refund?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>If the payment was made by 
                                Credit Card or Net-Banking, we can either issue Speedovation Credits or 
                                reverse credit to the Credit Card or credit your Net-Banking account. 
                                Speedovation Credits can be utilized on a future purchase on the website.</li>
                            <li>If the payment made was by Cash on Delivery, we can 
                                either issue Speedovation Credits or Bank Transfer. Speedovation Credits can be 
                                utilized on a future purchase on the website.</li>
                            <li>If Speedovation Credits were used to make a purchase, refund 
                                will only be issued as Speedovation Credits. This can be utilized on a future 
                                purchase on the website.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">How long will the refund process take?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Typically the refunds are 
                                initiated within 2 days of Product Inspection. Receipt of the refund 
                                would depend on the mode of payment chosen by you. The expected 
                                timelines are as below:<br><br>
                                <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5" border="1">
                                    <tbody>
                                        <tr>
                                            <th>Refund Method</th>
                                            <th>Refund Receipt Time (After Initiation)</th>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>Speedovation Credits</td>
                                            <td>1 business days</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>Bank Transfer/NEFT</td>
                                            <td>1-2 business days</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>Debit Card</td>
                                            <td>5-7 business days</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>Credit Card</td>
                                            <td>5-7 business days</td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </tbody>
                                </table>
                                <br>
                                For Debit Card and Credit Card transfers the time taken for 
                                refund depends finally on the bank. Though we would love to expedite the
                                same, our hands are tied. Also, you can assume additional delay for 
                                nationalised banks. Banks send an sms to customers for credit amount of 
                                more than Rs. 5000 only. In case your refund is less than Rs 5000 please
                                check your bank account or credit card account. </li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">How do I return a product?</p><div class="faq-content"><div>
                            <p>You can return a product hassle free in a few simple steps. However, do give us a call and we can help you with the steps to follow in case of return:</p>
                        </div>

                        <p>1) Place your item in its original packaging -  not the Speedovation.com box</p>
                        <p>2) Please mention your Name, Order Number, and Mobile Number, on the top of the box, and insert the original invoice</p>
                        <p>3) Keep the product and the package ready in case of a Speedovation Pick up</p>
                        <p>4) If you are sending it on your own make sure you seal it properly</p>

                        <div><p><b>You can choose to:</b></p></div>

                        <div>
                            <ul class="fl query-box faq-qustbox">
                                <li>
                                    <p class="faq-head">(a) Schedule a pickup using our logistics partner, at our cost, by calling us , or</p>
                                </li>

                                <li><p class="faq-head">Send it at your convenience to our address below and get a voucher for Courier charges up to a maximum of Rs 160 per kilogram of shipment.
                                        <br>
                                        Xerion Retail Pvt Ltd.<br>
                                        Returns Processing Centre &ndash; Front Office<br>
                                        Plot no. 109<br>
                                        Udyog Vihar, Phase 4<br>
                                        Gurgaon, Haryana, 122015<br>
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p class="faq-head">
                                        Scanned copy of courier slip needs to be emailed to us within 10 days of opening the return request.If we have received the product through courier, but we did not receive scanned copy of courier slip within 10 days of opening the return request, then we will reimburse a flat amount of Rs 100.
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p class="faq-head">
                                        It may also happen that our logistic partners may not have a pick up facility available in your area, even through it may have been delivered by them. Under such circumstances we hope you understand that we may request you to send it to our address as mentioned above in 4.(b)</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p class="faq-head">
                                        Drop Ship - We also offer you Returns Drop Ship facility for certain locations and constantly increasing our reach. Customers from these locations who would like to return their products can visit the centers and send their returns to Speedovation. This is provided to customers completely free of charge. Please get in touch with us to know if your location is served by this facility at this time.
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Where do I return my product?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Please check with our 
                                customer care if we cover your city for pickup and we do in most cases. 
                                If however your city is not covered or if you wish to send the product 
                                on your own please use this address. <br>
                                Xerion Retail Pvt Ltd.<br>
                                Returns Processing Centre &ndash; Front Office<br>
                                Plot no. 109<br>
                                Udyog Vihar, Phase 4<br>
                                Gurgaon, Haryana, 122015 </li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">I was charged shipping charges for my order. If I return my order, will I get back my shipping charge along with the refund?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li><strong>Shipping charge would not be included in the refund value of your order as this is a non-refundable charge.</strong></li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">I was charged a convenience charge for my 
                        COD order. If I return my order will I get back my convenience charge 
                        along with the refund?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Cash on Delivery convenience charge would not be included in the refund value of your order as this is a non-refundable charge.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">If I return a product on my own do I get back the shipping charges?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Once you incur courier 
                                charges please email us the scanned copy of the receipt within 10 days 
                                of the return. We will refund your courier charges up to a maximum of Rs
                                160 per kg. If you are unable to send the scanned copy of the receipt 
                                within 10 days of the return request, we will refund you a flat Rs 100 
                                against the courier charges.<br>
                                Refunds for courier charges are always in the mode of Speedovation Credits which can be redeemed on your future purchase.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">I was supposed to receive my refund by now but I haven't. What do I do?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>We update our customers 
                                through emails at every step of the returns process so please check for 
                                the last update from us in your email.<br>
                                If the last update states that the refund has already been 
                                initiated please wait for the refund process to complete. Depending on 
                                the mode of refund, the time taken for the refund to reflect in your 
                                account can vary. If you haven't received any update from us please 
                                write to us or give us a call.</li></ol><p></p></div></li></ul><div id="Drop Ship" class="clr"></div><h2>Drop Ship</h2><ul class="fl query-box faq-qustbox"><li><p class="faq-head">What is Drop Ship facility?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Drop ship is a facility where
                                customers can return their products to Speedovation without paying any 
                                processing fee or courier charges. <br>
                                Customers just need to visit our Drop ship centers with the 
                                product to be returned along with a Returns E-form and deposit the 
                                product at our Drop ship centers, so that the product reaches us safely.<br>
                                Refunds will be initiated post inspection once the shipment reaches our facility.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Can I Drop ship my returns at certain locations for Speedovation?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Speedovation has launched the 
                                Returns Drop Ship facility for certain locations. Customers from these 
                                locations who would like to return their products can visit the centers 
                                and send their returns to Speedovation.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Do I need to pay a fee for using this service?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>No. This service is completely free of charge.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Which all locations have the Drop Ship Facility?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Speedovation has launched Drop ship
                                facility for  certain cities and we are constantly increasing our 
                                reach. Please get in touch with us to know if we service your location 
                                at this time.</li></ol><p></p></div></li></ul><div id="Exchange Policy" class="clr"></div><h2>Exchange Policy</h2><ul class="fl query-box faq-qustbox"><li class=""><p class="faq-head">What is Speedovation.com's Exchange policy?</p><div class="faq-content" style="display: none;"><ol><li><b><u>Speedovation.com's 30 Day Exchange Policy</u></b><br>"No Questions Asked Exchange Policy!" <br><br>Though
                                we strive to give you a great customer experience each time you shop 
                                with us, if at all you are not 100% satisfied with your purchase, No 
                                Worries!!, you can buy any product in exchange to your previous order. <br><br>We mean what we say! All you need to do is give us a call on 0124-6128000 (24X7) or drop an email at <b><u><a href="mailto:care@Speedovation.com">care@Speedovation.com</a></u></b> within a period of 30 days, from the date of order. <br><br>However,
                                you must understand that we can't bear a loss either; so exchange of 
                                products will be accepted only if the products are returned in a 
                                saleable condition with the tags intact and in their original packaging,
                                in an unwashed and undamaged condition. C'mon that's just fair! </li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Which items can I exchange?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>All returnable items (except products from Speedovation partners) can be exchanged. To check which items cannot be exchanged, please call our customer care number on 0124-6128000 (24X7). We are constantly working to include more and more products to our exchange list. Please note that "Speedovation.com's 30 Day Exchange Policy" does not apply to Inner wear, Lingerie, Fragrances, Beauty products, Swimsuits, Jewellery(sold by Speedovation Partners only), Socks, Furniture, CDs, Pens and Books.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Is exchange available in my area?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Currently exchange is operational in areas where we can arrange pick up. Please give us a call on 0124-6128000 (24X7) to check if exchange is available in your area or not. We are working constantly to bring exchange in your area.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">What items can I buy in exchange?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Any product/s (except from Speedovation partners) can be bought in exchange. The final price of exchanged products should be equal to or more than the price of returned items.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">How soon can I expect the exchanged product?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Exchanged product is 
                                dispatched as soon as the returned item/s has passed product inspection.
                                Generally we won't take more than 72 hours after the pickup of returned
                                item/s is done. In case of any unexpected delay, we will keep you 
                                informed by email and SMS.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Can I exchange my product for an item of lesser value?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>No, your exchange order value should be equal to or more than the return item/s value.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Will I be charged for exchange?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>There is no charge for 
                                exchange. All you need to do is to return the original item and exchange
                                it for an item/s of same or higher value. In case you choose an item of
                                higher value, you can pay the differential amount as cash on delivery 
                                (COD). COD charges will be applicable. On products belonging to the 
                                Speedovation.com Add-on program, nominal shipping charges will be applicable. 
                                COD and shipping charges are non-refundable.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Can I buy multiple items in exchange for a single product?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>Yes, you can buy any number 
                                of items in exchange provided the final price of exchanged products 
                                should be equal to or more than the price of returned items.</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Can I re-exchange?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>If you are still dissatisfied with the product, you can again exchange the product for any item (covered in exchange policy).</li></ol><p></p></div></li><li><p class="faq-head">Can I cancel the exchange?</p><div class="faq-content"><ol><li>If you wish to cancel your 
                                exchange order, get in touch with Customer Care as soon as possible with
                                your order number. As long as your order has not been dispatched we can
                                cancel it and refund your amount in form of Speedovation Credits. <br><br>If 
                                your order has been dispatched but yet to be delivered, please do not 
                                accept delivery and contact Customer Care to inform them of the same. 
                                Refunds will be processed as per our Return policies. Any Speedovation Credits
